data.description: Experience the epitome of refined living in this meticulously maintained 4-bedroom Ranch nestled in the heart of Richmond Hill. Newly installed roof & siding, this home promises years of worry-free living! Upon entry, be greeted by the impeccable condition of the home, boasting upgrades at every turn. The kitchen dazzles with quartz countertops, subway tile backsplash & stainless steel appliances. Framed windows throughout & crown molding exuding sophistication, while LVP flooring adds elegance & practicality. Dining area charms w. shadow box trim & wood detailing enhancing the ambiance. Luxurious master suite, w. a spacious closet, trey ceilings & tranquil en-suite w. garden tub, separate shower & double sinks. Enjoy the beautifully landscaped exterior & screen patio boasting exceptional curb appeal. Community amenities abound, perfect for those seeking recreation options close to home. This home is a dream come true! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make it your own!
